#: src/glossary.md:3
msgid ""
"ML/AI/MLOps sohasidagi muhim terminlarning inglizcha-o'zbekcha lug'ati. Har "
"termin uchun **qisqacha izoh**va **kontekst**."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:5
msgid "A"
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:7
msgid ""
"**Activation function**(faollik funksiyasi) — neural network'da nonlinearity "
"qo'shadigan funksiya (ReLU, Sigmoid, Tanh)."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:8
msgid "**AdamW** — Adam optimizatori + better weight decay; modern default."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:9
msgid ""
"**Agent (AI Agent)** — LLM + tools + memory; goal'ga erishish uchun "
"ketma-ket harakatlar."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:10
msgid "**Anchor box** — object detection'da predefined bounding box shape."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:11
msgid ""
"**ANN (Approximate Nearest Neighbor)** — yaqin vektorlarni tez topish (HNSW, "
"IVF)."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:12
msgid "**API (Application Programming Interface)** — dasturlash interfeysi."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:13
msgid "**Async / await** — Python'da concurrent operations."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:14
msgid ""
"**Attention mechanism** — sequence'dagi muhim qismlarga \"diqqat\" qaratish."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:15
msgid ""
"**AUC (Area Under Curve)** — ROC curve ostidagi maydon (classification "
"metric)."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:16
msgid "**AutoGrad** — PyTorch'ning avtomatik gradient hisoblash mexanizmi."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:18
msgid "B"
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:20
msgid ""
"**Backpropagation** — gradient'larni orqaga tarqatish; neural network "
"o'rgatish algoritmi."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:21
msgid ""
"**Bagging (Bootstrap Aggregating)** — parallel ensemble (Random Forest "
"asosi)."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:22
msgid "**Batch** — bir vaqtda model'ga uzatilgan sample'lar to'plami."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:23
msgid ""
"**Batch Normalization (BN)** — activation'larni batch ichida "
"normallashtirish."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:24
msgid "**Bayesian Optimization** — smart hyperparameter qidiruv (Optuna)."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:25
msgid "**Bias (matematik)** — model output'iga qo'shiladigan constant."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:26
msgid "**Bias (xulosa)** — algoritmda noto'g'ri prediction'larga moyillik."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:27
msgid "**Boosting** — sequential ensemble (XGBoost, LightGBM)."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:28
msgid "**BPE (Byte-Pair Encoding)** — subword tokenization (GPT, Llama'da)."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:29
msgid ""
"**Broadcasting** — NumPy/PyTorch'da turli shape'dagi tensor'larga operatsiya."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:33
msgid "**Calibration** — model probability'larini ishonchli qilish."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:34
msgid "**Canary deployment** — yangi versiyani kichik traffic'da sinash."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:35
msgid "**Categorical feature** — diskret qiymatli feature (city, color)."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:36
msgid "**Chain-of-Thought (CoT)** — LLM'da step-by-step reasoning prompt."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:37
msgid "**Checkpoint** — model state saqlash (resume training uchun)."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:38
msgid "**Classification** — sample'ni diskret class'larga ajratish."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:39
msgid "**Clustering** — o'xshashlarni guruhlash (unsupervised)."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:40
msgid "**CNN (Convolutional NN)** — image processing uchun neural network."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:41
msgid "**Cold start** — yangi user/item haqida data yo'q muammosi."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:42
msgid ""
"**Concept drift** — input → output relationship vaqt o'tishi bilan "
"o'zgarishi."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:43
msgid "**Confusion Matrix** — TP, FP, TN, FN ko'rsatadigan jadval."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:44
msgid "**Context window** — LLM bir vaqtda ko'ra oladigan token soni."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:45
msgid "**Cosine similarity** — ikki vektor orasidagi cos burchak."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:46
msgid "**CRD (Custom Resource Definition)** — Kubernetes custom obyekt."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:47
msgid "**Cross-encoder** — sentence pair'lar uchun classifier (reranking'da)."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:48
msgid "**Cross-validation (CV)** — model'ni bir necha bo'lakda baholash."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:49
msgid "**CUDA** — NVIDIA GPU'larda parallel computation."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:51
msgid "D"
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:53
msgid "**DAG (Directed Acyclic Graph)** — Airflow'da workflow ko'rinishi."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:54
msgid "**Data augmentation** — sun'iy ravishda training data kengaytirish."
msgstr ""

#: src/glossary.md:55
msgid "**Data drift** — input distribution vaqt o'tishi bilan o'zgarishi."
